<TEXT>
<P>
I'm grateful that I saw Howard Rosenberg's enthusiastic review and took on the 
12-week commitment of "Game, Set and Match" on "Mystery!" Ian Holm's 
performance was so masterful that after one of his brilliant scenes, I found 
myself applauding the screen for the first time in 35 years of avid TV viewing. 
</P>
<P>
Meredith Brucker, San Marino 
</P>
