<HEADLINE>
<P>
CHINESE MASSACRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I just returned from a two-month stay in the Soviet Union. The Soviet 
television coverage of events in China was very thorough. 
</P>
<P>
A Soviet acquaintance told me that the reason for this coverage was to show the 
people in the Soviet Union what would happen to them if they started a serious 
rebellion. 
</P>
<P>
The commentary accompanying this coverage was chilling. I am glad to be back 
home. 
</P>
<P>
ADRIANNE PERRAULT 
</P>
<P>
Redondo Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
