<DATELINE>
<P>
OXFORD, Ohio 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A homemade gyrocopter crashed into a lake at Hueston Woods State Park on 
Saturday, killing two people, authorities said. Investigators were seeking the 
cause of the crash. 
