of the past, archeologists are unearthing the history of Israel. ; Photo, 
Safed, like other Israeli cities, has many ancient synagogues. ; Map, Israel, 
FRANK BURSINGER / Los Angeles Times ; Photo, An Israeli dude ranch could be the 
perfect respite for tourists who have already visited museums. BENJAMIN BYCEL; 
