but he was allowed to score on an interference ruling. ; Photo, West second 
baseman Pat DeBoer is unable to run down a ground ball in the third inning of 
the East's 13-5 victory Saturday at CSUN. GEORGE WILHELM / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
