<TEXT>
<P>
A chart accompanying Ruth Ryon's June 11 article, " 'Trophy Hotels': Record 
Sales Break All the Rules," contained an incorrect figure. The price per room 
at the 800-room Hyatt Regency, Maui, when it was sold in April, 1987, was 
$391,000. 
</P>
