<HEADLINE>
<P>
FRANKE FINISHES THIRD IN PREP DISCUS EVENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Canyon High School's Allison Franke, The Times' female track athlete of the 
year in Orange County, finished third in the discus at the Keebler 
International Prep Invitational track and field meet Saturday in Elmhurst, Ill. 
Franke had a throw of 151-feet-3. Dory Reeves of Spokane was first with a throw 
of 157-8. 
</P>
</TEXT>
